<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (Moved in ``s'' category) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BBA-GEORGE-COLUMN (Undated) _ Sports of The Times column on Joe
Torre, the man who stays out of the Yankees' way. By Thomas George.
</P>
<P>
   CAR-GORDON (Undated) _ Jeff Gordon is going for the modern-day
NASCAR record of five straight victories when he races on Saturday
night in Bristol, Tenn. By Tarik El-Bashir.
</P>
