new standard? Does no fibbing about peccadilloes mean we have to
settle bar tabs on time? Let's be reasonable!''
</P>
<P>
   Typo interjects, ``Moot question, Boss! Floyd the Barmaid has
you holy on debts since her neck size went to 19!''
</P>
<P>
