<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-08-20 13:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3369 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HOME-CULDESAC-2TAKES-     08-20 1043
