his rage lie in the 1980s, when he worked side by side with the CIA
backing the Afghan rebels. When that battle was over, he and his
fellow holy warriors _ having defeated the British in the 19th
century and the Soviets in the 20th _ went to work on the United
States. By Tim Weiner.
