should be dismissed. Attorneys are presenting oral arguments on
Coca-Cola's motion to dismiss Pepsico's lawsuit accusing Coca-Cola
of using illegal tactics to dominate the $54 billion U.S.
soft-drink business. (Gramig, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8
p.m. ET.
