1998 (the first opens next week), the company plans to open three
additional stores in Chile in fiscal 1999 and open its first store
in Buenos Aires, Argentina in the fourth quarter of fiscal 1999.
Will include background on Depot's main competition in Chile,
Sodimac, which recently opened its first U.S. office in Atlanta to
handle U.S. supplies. (Bond, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8
p.m. ET.
</P>
