It was made to speak to you.'' So says Dr. Beer, aka Brian Nummer,
who owns the Athens Brewing Company and holds a Ph.D. in food
microbiology. Nummer will be teaching a course this fall at the
University of Georgia called ``the art, science, &AMP; history of
beer,'' and he expects students to learn enough in the class to
open their own brewpubs, or, at the very least, to better
appreciate a fine draw of homemade beer. (McCarthy, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) WITH PHOTO.
