Settlement, 466 Grand Street, lower East Side. A drama directed by
Ellen Beckerman. 5 p.m. Also Saturday at 7 p.m.; Sunday and Monday
at 9:30 p.m.; Thursday at 5:30 and 10:45 p.m.; Aug. 28 at 9:45 p.m.
and Aug. 29 at noon.
