<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-SPORTS-BUDGET(SLANG) </SLUG>
  
The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
Aug. 21 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at the Daily News, (818) 713-3602.
<TEXT>
<P>
   BBN-DODGERS-MARLINS (Miami) _ The Los Angeles Dodgers face the
Florida Marlins at 4:05 p.m. PDT.
</P>
<P>
   By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBN-DODGERNOTES (Miami) _ Notebook from the Dodgers-Marlins
game.
</P>
<P>
   By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   BBA-ANGELS-TIGERS (Anaheim, Calif.) _ The Anaheim Angels face
the Detroit Tigers at 7:35 p.m. PDT.
</P>
<P>
   By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.)
</P>
<P>
   FBC-CROUSE-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Column on UCLA quarterback
Cade McNown.
</P>
<P>
   By Karen Crouse. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.)
