<HEADER>
A4509 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-USSTRIKES-AFGHANISTAN     08-20 0532
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-USSTRIKES-AFGHANISTAN-0821-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    AFGHANISTAN: WHERE IT IS, WHAT IT'S LIKE
 &HT;    With USSTRIKES-MAIN-0821.
 &HT;    By ANDREW MOLLISON 
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service 
