<P>
   CLINTON-AIRSTRIKES (Washington) _ U.S. forces carry out air
strikes against targets in Afghanistan and Sudan in retaliation for
the embassy bombings in Africa and to prevent future attacks,
President Clinton says. Clinton interrupt his vacation in
Massachusetts to return to Washington for meetings with his
