as he is. ... I've always liked the way he delivers.''
</P>
<P>
   _ `` &UR; Barbara Walters &LR;  was _ and is _ a very sexy babe. ... She
is a profoundly sensual, very female being with a great body.''
</P>
<P>
   Meanwhile,  &UR; Warren St. John  &LR; of the New York Observer describes
Rivera's on-air fascination with the current presidential scandal
as the natural outgrowth of his earlier incarnations. ``Mr. Rivera
