   WAGGING-TONGUES (Los Angeles) _ With images of the film ``Wag
the Dog'' popping into heads as President Clinton announced the
U.S. had bombed two countries as Monica Lewinsky testified before a
federal grand jury, it was just another incident of the cynicism
bred from the merging of Hollywood and reality. By Bob Strauss.
Daily News Film Writer. (Will move in the ``a'' national news file,
