genetically developed drug as part of a nationwide study. ``I'm
hoping it will find a cure and put an end to this epidemic,'' said
Jeff Linden, 33, a Los Angeles-area resident. By Yvette Cabrera.
(Will move in the ``a'' national news file and the ``n'' California
news file.) &QL;
