<SLUG> BC-AZR-BUDGET-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 BC-ADD-BUDGET-AZR 
  
 (For use by New York Times News Service clients) 
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic editorial has been added for use
by clients of the NYTimes News Service for Friday, Aug. 21. If you
have any questions, please contact the Republic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
</P>
<P>
   EDIT-TERROR (Undated) - So much for the experts. The pundits
proclaimed the Clinton administration was on the ropes, the
president about to collapse in the far corner of the ring.
</P>
<P>
   But never - ever - count Bill Clinton out. Alas, the fates
handed him an opportunity for some redemption in presidential
leadership, and he did not disappoint. Story moved in the ``K``
category. &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
