<HEADLINE>
&HT;     
 &HT;    
 &HT;      REPUBLICANS SAY WAR ON TERRORISM IS JUST BEGINNING; 
 &HT;      DISPUTE ``WAG-THE-DOG'' ANALOGY
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;     By Ronald F. Eckstein  
 &HT;    c. 1998 States News Service  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON, August 20 -- The American war on terrorism is just
beginning, according to Congressional Republican leaders, and
