<HEADLINE>
LIVENT DREW IN A NEW TEAM DESPITE JUGGLING EXPENSES 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: N.Y., Canada)  (Eds: Also filed in ``f'' category.) 
(ART ADV: Photos are being sent to NYT photo clients. A graphic is
being sent to NYT graphics clients. Non-subscribers can make
individual purchase by calling (888) 603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
